<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我聽說，<delay8 />如果想嘗試新的事物，<delay20 />
從春天開始是最適合喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay20 />我也正在認真思考，<delay20 />
今年要不要試著<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發掘一些<delay8 />新的興趣呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一旦習慣了這種高溫，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就覺得這樣也不錯呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為天氣很熱的時候，<delay20 />
就會覺得冰涼的冰紅茶特別好喝！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到秋天，就會想到讀書之秋呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想<delay8 />趁著這個機會，<delay20 />
挑戰之前很少閱讀的<delay8 />書籍種類喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">冬天的時候，<delay8 /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總是會特別想吃<delay20 />
熱～騰騰的料理呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近也在研究<delay8 />新口味的<delay8 />火鍋料理喔～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是完成了，<delay8 />到時候再請大家
一起來吃吃看吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近越來越有春天的感覺了呢！<delay frames="40" />
宜人的暖風徐徐吹來，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我心情也特別好喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夏天<delay8 />總讓人覺得心情很舒暢呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要不要也試著發表一下<delay20 />
自己寫的詩呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">秋天<delay8 />有種浪漫的氛圍呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蟲鳴聲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />染上秋色的樹葉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />好像能寫出一首好詩喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />冬天總會覺得手腳很冷對吧～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過只要活動一下手腳，身體就會暖和起來，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我也得努力散步才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
