	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天氣變暖之後，<delay8 />常常能看到昆蟲的蹤影呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />連我都因為天氣很好，<delay20 />
所以到戶外逛逛了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得春天<delay8 />有種特別的氛圍呢。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會讓人覺得輕飄飄<delay8 />又軟綿綿的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你能體會我說的這種感覺嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
這段時期天氣特別炎熱，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請一定要好好補充水分喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夏天<delay20 />有種獨特的氛圍對吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起中午，這個時間更容易體會<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說的感覺喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近越來越有秋天的感覺了，<delay20 />
連這個時間也讓人覺得很舒適呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別適合細細品味讀書的樂趣喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有股秋天的氣息呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道為什麼，只要感受到這氛圍<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就會變得多愁善感……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">冬天雖然很冷，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過和晚上比起來，<delay8 />早上溫暖多了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實還是挺冷的……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種清新<delay20 />又冷冽的氣息<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概就是冬天獨有的味道吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
